snippet.title: sfäre in action (PC)
snippet.description:
Sfäre is an experimental project I have been working on for quite some time now. I'm not sure who it is intended for, but it's pretty relaxing and chill.
Get it on ItchIO: https://falkenbrew.itch.io/sfre
